00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:46.440
Bu, aku akan menjelaskan
semuanya padamu!

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:47.880
Ayo pergi!

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:02.040
Kemana Rimjhim membawa bibinya?

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:20.480
Rimjhim, kemana kamu membawaku?

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:23.560
Bu, ikut aku!  - Apa maksudmu?

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:25.320
Tempat apa ini?

